('2006', '26', 'Omen', 'The Omen is an Attack Cruiser designed for fast aggressive combat.\r\n<br><font size="14"><b>Traits</b></font>\r\n<b><a href=showinfo:3335>Amarr Cruiser</a> skill bonus per level:</b>\r\n10% bonus to Medium Energy Turret capacitor use\r\n5% bonus to Medium Energy Turret rate of fire\r\n<br><font size="14"><b>Development</b></font>\r\nThe Omen is a stereotypical example of the Amarrian School of thinking when it comes to ship design: thick armor and hard hitting lasers. Advancements in heat dissipation allow the Omen to fire its lasers faster than other ships without this technology.', '', '11650000', '118000', '400', '1', '4', '4527500', '74'),
