('2811', '657', 'Inferno Rage Torpedo', 'An ultra-heavy plasma missile. While it is a slow projectile, its sheer damage potential is simply staggering.\r\n\r\nThis modified version of the Inferno Torpedo packs a considerably stronger punch, but as a result is heavier and slower. This makes it very effective against larger targets, but markedly less effective against smaller and more agile targets.', '21_06', '1000', '0.1', '0', '5000', '0', '1440720', '931'),
