('2831', '226', 'Serpentis Fortress', 'This gigantic station is one of the Serpentis military installations and a black jewel of the alliance between The Guardian Angels and The Serpentis Corporation. Even for its size, it has no commercial station services or docking bays to receive guests.', '', '100000', '100000000', '10000', '1', '8', '0', '0'),
