('2991', '314', 'Crate of Amarr Scripture Educational Study Packages (Matari translation)', 'These study materials provide a guide through the structure and meanings of Amarr holy texts in a way that school-age children can easily understand. Education, like every other aspect of daily life in the Empire, is closely tied into religion, and by the time they leave school, Amarr children are expected to have a working and in-depth understanding of their way of life.<br><br>\r\nThese particular copies have been carefully translated by experts into painfully precise Matari for distribution in the Republic.', '50_11', '10', '10', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0'),
